children.text: Synaia Consulting collects and utilizes data solely for the purpose of enhancing our services and providing tailored solutions to our clients. We ensure that all data is handled in compliance with relevant data protection laws. Users must ensure that any data provided is accurate and lawful. Unauthorized use or sharing of data without consent is strictly prohibited. By using our services, you consent to our data practices as outlined in our policy.

Synaia Consulting is committed to protecting your privacy. We collect only necessary personal information and use it to improve our services. Your data is stored securely and will not be shared with third parties without your explicit consent, except as required by law. You have the right to access, modify, and delete your personal information at any time. By using our services, you agree to our privacy practices as described in this policy.
